org.jgentleframework.services.datalocator.data
Interface Key<T>

Type Parameters:
T - 
public interface Key<T>

Key instance represents all information of its includes key name, created date, modified date, parent key, ... and contains sub keys, values if they exist.

Note: Generic Type effect only to its values but no effect to its sub keys.

Author:
LE QUOC CHUNG - mailto: skydunkpro@yahoo.com
